{"type":"message","id":"a87b0202","parentId":"03e3fecc","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:06:28.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **EGX Market Analysis Complete**\n\n**Current Status:**\n- EGX30 Index: 47,786 points\n- Today's change: -48.62 points (-0.10%)\n- Monthly performance: +14.51%\n- Market cap: 3 trillion EGP\n\n**Analysis:**\n✅ Strong upward momentum\n🏦 Banking sector: Strong gains\n🏗️ Real estate: Leading sector\n\n**Recommendation:**\n🎯 **Buy now** in banking and real estate sectors\n⏰ Best entry: During intraday pullbacks\n🔄 Target: Next resistance levels\n\nThe market shows positive momentum with banking and real estate leading. Good entry points are during pullbacks within the uptrend."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"arcee-ai/trinity-large-preview:free","usage":{"input":19899,"output":140,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772244378597}}
