**GB AUTO**] | 26.60 | 26.75 | 25.75 | +2.98% | 1.24M | [aa.aa] | 07:16:59 |\n| [**Madinet Nasr for Housing and Development**] | 4.16 | 4.18 | 4.15 | +0.24% | 3.38M | [aa.aa] | 07:16:59 |\n| [**Oriental Weavers**] | 22.70 | 22.79 | 22.57 | +0.40% | 725.49K | [aa.aa] | 07:16:59 |\n| [**Raya Holding**] | 3.79 | 3.79 | 3.58 | +5.28% | 24.18M | [aa.aa] | 07:16:59 |\n| [**Abu Qir Fertilizers and Chemical Industries**] | 50.50 | 50.50 | 49.08 | +3.02% | 548.3K | [aa.a\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772244450666}}
