{"type":"message","id":"a975139e","parentId":"bd029e5e","timestamp":"2026-02-28T02:12:03.866Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-96520ef2f830a104","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: 10 Egyptian stocks outperform gold, real estate, and savings certificates in Q2 2025\nAuthor: Daily News Egypt\nURL: https://www.dailynewsegypt.com/2025/07/06/10-egyptian-stocks-outperform-gold-real-estate-and-savings-certificates-in-q2-2025/\nText: 10 Egyptian stocks outperform gold, real estate, and savings certificates in Q2 2025 - Dailynewsegypt\n[\n![Dailynewsegypt]![Dailynewsegypt]![Dailynewsegypt] ] \nFebruary 28, 2026\n[\n** ] \n[**] [**] [**] [**] [**] \n[\n** ] \n****\n[Font Resizer**Aa**] \n**\n**\n[\n] \n[\n![Dailynewsegypt]![Dailynewsegypt] ] \n[**] \n[Font Resizer**Aa**] \n**\n**\n* [Home] \n* [Business] \n* [Politics] \n* [Interviews] \n* [Culture] \n* [Opinion] \n* [Sports] \n* [Lifestyle] \nSearch\n****\nFollow US\n[**] [**] [**] [**] [**] \n[Dailynewsegypt] &gt; [Blog] &gt; [Business] &gt; [Stock Market] &gt; 10 Egyptian stocks outperform gold, real estate, and savings certificates in Q2 2025\n[Business] [Stock Market] \n# 10 Egyptian stocks outperform gold, real estate, and savings certificates in Q2 2025\n![Daily News Egypt] \nLast updated: July 6, 2025 10:15 am\n[Daily News Egypt] \n**Share\n[**\n] \n[\n**] \n[**\n] \n[**\n] \n[**] \n2 Min Read\n![10 Egyptian stocks outperform gold, real estate, and savings certificates in Q2 2025] \n**SHARE\n[**\n] \n[\n**] \n[**\n] \n[**\n] \n[**] \nTen stocks listed on the Egyptian Exchange (EGX) posted exceptional gains during the second quarter of 2025, with share prices soaring by more than 70%—significantly outperforming traditional investment options such as gold, real estate, and bank savings certificates. The rally was fuelled by a combination of strong financial results and speculative trading, particularly in small- and mid-cap stocks.\nAmong the top gainers, U Consum